to charge you money for it. And so having this sort of head of AI, people that are responsible

00:13:48.799 --> 00:13:55.039
for being that expert kind of prevents this like, I call it like AI grift, but like you basically

00:13:55.039 --> 00:13:59.520
prevent these, these grift organizations from getting in and start extracting money. When in

00:13:59.520 --> 00:14:03.679
