00:43:19.199 --> 00:43:25.040
model. You get a bunch of images of cats and dogs, and then you have the picture of the cat,

00:43:25.040 --> 00:43:29.199
and you say, that's a cat. You get a picture of the dog, that's a dog. You give enough examples

