00:49:41.600 --> 00:49:46.239
take to build that internally? What are the functional requirements of it? Are we supporting

00:49:46.239 --> 00:49:52.000
10 people or 10,000, right? Do we have the skills internally to build it? How quickly is the answer

00:49:52.000 --> 00:49:57.919
